05:21.333 --> 05:24.541
I really appreciate all of your messages

05:24.666 --> 05:26.125
and I'm still here.

05:27.291 --> 05:32.125
And I just got to this amazing place,

05:32.875 --> 05:35.916
'cause I'm going to be getting
back to writing this week,

05:36.041 --> 05:37.583
so stay tuned.

05:39.166 --> 05:40.041
Oh.

05:41.333 --> 05:42.333
Score!

05:42.458 --> 05:45.375
And I have a porch swing, so,

05:46.208 --> 05:47.708
everything's gonna be fine.

05:49.125 --> 05:52.583
(plucky country music)

06:04.916 --> 06:08.958
(construction tools buzzing)

06:12.333 --> 06:13.458
